definition: to produce (by natural growth, or by manufacture, mining etc)/to yield/to turn out/produce/products

to go out/to come out/to occur/to produce/to go beyond/to rise/to put forth/to happen/(used after a verb to indicate an outward direction or a positive result)/classifier for dramas, plays, operas etc

sentences.english: Thellonking is one of the most productive activities a human being can undertake.
sentences.chinese: 念考是此中最出產性活動己的總稱能夠舉行。

sentences.english: My favorite beer is from a microbrewery.
sentences.chinese: 我最喜歡的啤酒是一家小釀酒廠出產的。

sentences.english: Buzzing insects will infest all your trees and the crops of your soil.
sentences.chinese: 害蟲要吃盡你所有的樹木和土地的出產。

sentences.english: Kentucky farms produce some of the world's finest pure breed horses.
sentences.chinese: 肯塔基州農場出產一些世界上最好的純種馬。

sentences.english: The Mosel valley produces the best grapes for Germany's most famous wine, Riesling.
sentences.chinese: 此酒選用摩塞爾山谷出產的優質雷司令葡萄釀製而成。

sentences.english: New product line may decide location to be in Sichuan Chengdu.
sentences.chinese: 新出產線可能定址在四川成都。

sentences.english: Alberta also produces more coal than any other province.
sentences.chinese: 阿爾伯達出產的煤也多於其他任何省份。

sentences.english: Made with grapes from the prestigious Maipo Valley, This wine has an intense ruby red colour, and possesses an intense aroma of spices and chocolate.
sentences.chinese: 選用邁坡山谷出產的美樂葡萄釀製而成的這款乾紅。

sentences.english: "urgent" out of ChanXu delimit a single class output and hang express CARDS.
sentences.chinese: “急件”出產需劃定出單班產量，並掛急件牌。

sentences.english: Longjing tea, also known as Dragon Well tea, is a famous variety of green tea grown in Hangzhou in Zhejiang province.
sentences.chinese: 龍井茶是指浙江杭州出產的系列綠茶。

sentences.english: Thee Annin flag company makes most American flags.
sentences.chinese: 安寧國旗公司出產全美大部分的國旗。

sentences.english: We are specialized in silky fowl and food products.
sentences.chinese: 我們專門出產真空包裝烏骨雞和一般食品。

sentences.english: Zhejiang Shangsen Industry & Trade Co. , Ltd. specialized in producing interior ShangsenPVC door.
sentences.chinese: 浙江尚森工貿有限企業專業出產室內免漆門。

sentences.english: Although China has coal supplies, they are of low quality
sentences.chinese: 儘管中國自身出產煤炭資源，質量卻相當低。

sentences.english: This domain also produces a Vermentino, Merlot and Syrah.
sentences.chinese: 該區域還出產韋爾芒提諾，美樂及西拉葡萄酒。

sentences.english: Huzhou Crape is a kind of rugged silk produced in Zhejiang with a light texture.
sentences.chinese: 湖縐是浙江出產的一種有皺紋的絲織品，質地輕盈。
